02321 //*****************************************************************************
02322 //
02323 // The following are defines for the bit fields in the WDT_O_LOAD register.
02324 //
02325 //*****************************************************************************
02326 #define WDT_LOAD_M              0xFFFFFFFF  // Watchdog Load Value
02327 #define WDT_LOAD_S              0
02328 
02329 //*****************************************************************************
02330 //
02331 // The following are defines for the bit fields in the WDT_O_VALUE register.
02332 //
02333 //*****************************************************************************
02334 #define WDT_VALUE_M             0xFFFFFFFF  // Watchdog Value
02335 #define WDT_VALUE_S             0
02336 
02337 //*****************************************************************************
02338 //
02339 // The following are defines for the bit fields in the WDT_O_CTL register.
02340 //
02341 //*****************************************************************************
02342 #define WDT_CTL_WRC             0x80000000  // Write Complete
02343 #define WDT_CTL_INTTYPE         0x00000004  // Watchdog Interrupt Type
02344 #define WDT_CTL_RESEN           0x00000002  // Watchdog Reset Enable
02345 #define WDT_CTL_INTEN           0x00000001  // Watchdog Interrupt Enable
02346 
02347 //*****************************************************************************
02348 //
02349 // The following are defines for the bit fields in the WDT_O_ICR register.
02350 //
02351 //*****************************************************************************
02352 #define WDT_ICR_M               0xFFFFFFFF  // Watchdog Interrupt Clear
02353 #define WDT_ICR_S               0
02354 
02355 //*****************************************************************************
02356 //
02357 // The following are defines for the bit fields in the WDT_O_RIS register.
02358 //
02359 //*****************************************************************************
02360 #define WDT_RIS_WDTRIS          0x00000001  // Watchdog Raw Interrupt Status
02361 
02362 //*****************************************************************************
02363 //
02364 // The following are defines for the bit fields in the WDT_O_MIS register.
02365 //
02366 //*****************************************************************************
02367 #define WDT_MIS_WDTMIS          0x00000001  // Watchdog Masked Interrupt Status
02368 
02369 //*****************************************************************************
02370 //
02371 // The following are defines for the bit fields in the WDT_O_TEST register.
02372 //
02373 //*****************************************************************************
02374 #define WDT_TEST_STALL          0x00000100  // Watchdog Stall Enable
02375 
02376 //*****************************************************************************
02377 //
02378 // The following are defines for the bit fields in the WDT_O_LOCK register.
02379 //
02380 //*****************************************************************************
02381 #define WDT_LOCK_M              0xFFFFFFFF  // Watchdog Lock
02382 #define WDT_LOCK_UNLOCKED       0x00000000  // Unlocked
02383 #define WDT_LOCK_LOCKED         0x00000001  // Locked
02384 #define WDT_LOCK_UNLOCK         0x1ACCE551  // Unlocks the watchdog timer

02425                                             // and may be modified

02427                                             // and may not be modified

04732                                             // configuration

04738                                             // value selects the 16-bit timer
04739                                             // configuration

10037                                             // completed to meet 1% accuracy

10039                                             // failed to meet 1% accuracy
10040 #define SYSCTL_PIOSCSTAT_CT_M   0x0000007F  // Calibration Trim Value
10041 #define SYSCTL_PIOSCSTAT_DT_S   16
10042 #define SYSCTL_PIOSCSTAT_CT_S   0

11624                                 0x00000001  // Basic

11626                                 0x00000002  // Auto-Request
11627 #define UDMA_CHCTL_XFERMODE_PINGPONG                                          \
11628                                 0x00000003  // Ping-Pong
11629 #define UDMA_CHCTL_XFERMODE_MEM_SG                                            \
11630                                 0x00000004  // Memory Scatter-Gather
11631 #define UDMA_CHCTL_XFERMODE_MEM_SGA                                           \
11632                                 0x00000005  // Alternate Memory Scatter-Gather
11633 #define UDMA_CHCTL_XFERMODE_PER_SG                                            \
11634                                 0x00000006  // Peripheral Scatter-Gather
11635 #define UDMA_CHCTL_XFERMODE_PER_SGA                                           \
11636                                 0x00000007  // Alternate Peripheral
11637                                             // Scatter-Gather
11638 #define UDMA_CHCTL_XFERSIZE_S   4
